OL,3,CEx-Kazakhstani minister sentenced to
OL,4,C24 years for torturing and murdering
OL,5,Cwife
OL,7,FSome people may find some of the
OL,8,Fdetails in this story distressing.
OL,10,FA former government official has been
OL,11,Fsentenced to 24 years in prison for
OL,12,Ftorturing and murdering his wife in a
OL,13,Flandmark case.
OL,15,FSaltanat Nukenova, 31, was found dead
OL,16,Fin November in a restaurant owned by
OL,17,Fone of her husband's relatives.
