OL,3,CEx-Kazakhstani minister sentenced to
OL,4,C24 years for torturing and murdering
OL,5,Cwife
OL,7,FKuandyk Bishimbayev, Kazakhstan's
OL,8,Fformer economy minister, maintained
OL,9,Fhis innocence before admitting in
OL,10,Fcourt last month that he had beaten
OL,11,Fher and "unintentionally" caused her
OL,12,Fdeath.
OL,14,FHis lawyers initially disputed medical
OL,15,Fevidence indicating Ms Nukenova died
OL,16,Ffrom blows to the head.
OL,18,FBishimbayev's relative, Bakhytzhan
OL,19,FBaizhanov, was sentenced to four years
OL,20,Fin prison for helping Bishimbayev
OL,21,Fcover up the murder.
