OL,3,CEx-Kazakhstani minister sentenced to
OL,4,C24 years for torturing and murdering
OL,5,Cwife
OL,7,FDays after Ms Nukenova's death, her
OL,8,Frelatives launched an online petition
OL,9,Furging authorities to pass "Saltanat's
OL,10,FLaw" to bolster protection for those
OL,11,Fat risk of domestic violence.
OL,13,FIt quickly got over 150,000
OL,14,Fsignatures. As the trial began, more
OL,15,Fthan 5,000 Kazakhs wrote senators
OL,16,Furging tougher laws on abuse, Kazakh
OL,17,Fmedia said.
OL,19,FDuring the trial, thousands of people
OL,20,Furged the authorities to adopt harsher
OL,21,Fpenalties for domestic violence.
