OL,3,CEx-Kazakhstani minister sentenced to
OL,4,C24 years for torturing and murdering
OL,5,Cwife
OL,7,FBishimbayev's trial was the first in
OL,8,Fthe country to be streamed online and,
OL,9,Fas a result, sparked a stream of
OL,10,Fdebate on social media.
OL,12,FCCTV footage serving as a key piece of
OL,13,Fevidence in the trial was also shown,
OL,14,Fand it was particularly disturbing.
OL,16,FBishimbayev is seen dragging his wife
OL,17,Fby her hair, and then punching and
OL,18,Fkicking her. Hours after it was
OL,19,Frecorded, she died of brain trauma.
