OL,5,Cwife
OL,7,FAccording to a 2018 study backed by UN
OL,8,FWomen, about 400 women die from
OL,9,Fdomestic violence each year in
OL,10,FKazakhstan, although many cases go
OL,11,Funreported.
OL,13,FIn 2017, Kazakhstan decriminalised
OL,14,Fbeatings and other acts causing
OL,15,F"minor" physical damage, making them
OL,16,Fpunishable only by fines or short jail
OL,17,Fterms.
