OL,7,FKazakhstan has since reversed its law
OL,8,Fsince the trial began, increasing
OL,9,Fpenalties and introducing new criminal
OL,10,Foffences including harassment of
OL,11,Fminors.
OL,13,FSenate Speaker Maulen Ashimbayev said
OL,14,Fthat properly implementing the new law
OL,15,Fadopted in the wake of the trial will
OL,16,Frequire "a great deal of work,"
OL,17,Fincluding educational campaigns in
OL,18,Fschools and the media as well as
OL,19,Fvigilance from civil society groups.
